00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:27,680
 Now if you're in ancient Hebrew

357
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:29,400
 and you're reading the book of Jonah,

358
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:32,120
 when you say, oh, this is a prophetical book,

