00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,120
 So at the beginning of the book,

372
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:08,840
 God sends Jonah a message.

373
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:12,200
 It says, "And the word of the Lord came to Jonah.

